  <h2 class="heading">The Enderwalk Archives is a place for MCYT (Minecraft YouTube) fanworks, including fan fiction based on roleplays, Let’s Plays, other fanworks, other media, and real-person fiction (RPF).</h2>

  <h3 class="heading">What We Believe</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Our goal is maximum inclusiveness of content that falls within the Archive’s scope and content policies.</li>
    <li>We do not sell the data that you post on, submit to or share on the Enderwalk Archives to third parties, and we do not include or accept paid advertisements from third parties.</li>
    <li>By using the Enderwalk Archives, you agree to follow the content rules of the Archive, or otherwise risk having your account terminated.</li>
    <li>The staff of the Enderwalk Archives are not liable for any legal risks you face by posting, viewing, or otherwise engaging with content posted to the Archive. We do not claim legal responsibility over your posted content, and you are entirely responsible for your own content.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3 class="heading">The Rules:</h3>
